quran[19{c,v,t}:
19,77,Afara'aytal lazee kafara bi Aayaatinaa wa qaala la oota yanna maalanw wa waladaa
19,78,Attala'al ghaiba amitta khaza'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa
19,79,Kallaa; sanaktubu maa yaqoolu wa namuddu lahoo minal 'azaabi maddaa
19,80,Wa narisuhoo maa yaqoolu wa yaateenaa fardaa
19,81,Wattakhazoo min doonil laahi aalihatal liyakoonoo lahum 'izzaa
19,82,Kallaa; sa yakfuroona bi'ibaadatihim wa yakoonoona 'alaihim diddaa (section 9)
19,83,Alam tara annaaa arsalnash Shayaateena 'alal kaafireena ta'uzzuhum azzaa
19,84,Falaa ta'jal alaihim innamaa na 'uddu lahum 'addaa
19,85,Yawma nahshurul muttaqeena ilar Rahmaani wafdaa
19,86,Wa nasooqul mujrimeena ilaa Jahannama wirdaa
19,87,Laa yamlikoonash shafaa'ta illaa manittakhaza 'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa
19,88,Wa qaalut takhazar Rahmaanu waladaa
19,89,Laqad ji'tum shai'an iddaa
19,90,Takaadus samaawaatu yatafattarna minhu wa tanshaq qul ardu wa takhirrul jibaalu haddaa
19,91,An da'aw lir Rahmaani waladaa
19,92,Wa maa yambaghee lir Rahmaani ai yattakhiza waladaa
19,93,In kullu man fis samaawaati wal ardi illaaa aatir Rahmaani 'abdaa
19,94,Laqad ahsaahum wa addahum 'addaa
19,95,Wa kulluhum aateehi Yawmal Qiyaamati fardaa
